    "en": {
      "title": "600 prisoners escape from Kandakadu Rehabilitation Center",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "About 1,000 prisoners are being held at the Kandakadu Rehabilitation Center under the Commissioner General of Rehabilitation.",
        "Meanwhile, a prisoner was killed in a clash between two groups there last night.",
        "Police spokesman Senior Superintendent of Police Nihal Taltuwa said 600 prisoners had escaped the clash.",
        "He said other detainees were protesting and did not allow police or security forces to enter."
      ],
